metadata.title: New Complete Tractor OSGR Replacement Starter 1400-0120 Compatible with/Replacement for John Deere 2056 Combine, 2058 Combine, 2064 Combine, 2066 Combine, 2256 Combine, 2258 Combine TY6617, TY6618
features: Specs: Starter, 12v, 11 tooth, 4.8KW, OSGR type w/three (3) ear mount. Can replace DD type 1400-0108. Note, check clearance on some JD 4020 models, may have interference issues on starter motor height when models w/drop type manifold is used.
Replaces OEM Numbers: Atlantic (Prior) - 1400-0106, X-SND0234, X-SND0398, John Deere - TY6617, TY6618, TY6701, TY6713, X-2-3114-ND, X-A-RE41875, X-A-TY6701, X-S-8033, X-SND0234, X-TS-1390

Compatible With/Replacement For: John Deere - 2056 Combine; 2058 Combine; 2064 Combine; 2066 Combine; 2256 Combine; 2258 Combine; 2264 Combine; 2266 Combine; 300 Indust/Const; 300A Indust/Const; 300B Indust/Const; 300C Indust/Const; 300D Indust/Const; 301 Indust/Const; 301A Indust/Const; 302 Indust/Const; 3020; 302A Indust/Const; 3510 Cane Harvester; 4020; 4030; 4040; 4045D Eng; 4045H Eng; 4045T Eng; 4050; 4055; 4230; 4250; 4255; 4320 Compact Tractor; 4430; 444 Indust/Const; 4440
